  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dba\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0daf\u0dd3 \u0dad\u0dd1\u0d9c\u0dca\u0d9c\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dab\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Mohini, who gave a gift in the plane, was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kalutara South Police said that the woman who gave a 2-year-old male child to a person identified at the airport and ran away was arrested early today (29).",
        "Police say that the arrested woman is a 37-year-old resident of Galle, Udugama area.",
        "According to the instructions of Chief Inspector Suneth Shanta, a police team arrested the suspect woman at her home.",
        "A senior police officer also said that the investigation so far has revealed that she is married with other children.",
        "The suspect has been arrested based on a complaint made by a person residing in Bodhiawatta, Kalutara who came to the island on the 25th after working in Saudi Arabia for about 11 years.",
        "The police said that the complainant stated that while the complainant was returning to the mother country after working in Saudi Arabia, he identified Kathak who came with a 2-year-old boy on the same flight, and at the Katunayake airport, the complainant stated that she also wanted to go to Kalutara, so she and the child had been picked up in the same taxi. .",
        "The police said that while coming from Katunayake to Kalutara, the complaint noted that the child got out of the vehicle after saying that he was bringing a bottle of soft drink and a chocolate in Kalutara and did not return for a long time."
      ],
